data.text:
Skinner, Cornelia O.

New York, NY: Not published, 1948. First Edition. Unbound. Near fine condition. Item #002710

Cornelia Otis Skinner (1910-1979). 4 1/2" wide x 3 3/8" tall card, signed boldly "Cornelia Otis Skinner" and dated "Nov. 6th, 48 New York City." Card has a printed line which she signed her name upon, as well as printed lines for the date and place. An attractive signature, suitable for framing.
